clear.code              Creates a file copying current code without
                        comments and tabuations
copypaste               A function to import copied data in RStudio via
                        clipboard, the use of Addins is also highly
                        recommended
libraries               Compiles and installs all libraries in the
                        current RStudio script where the word library
                        is written
r.args                  Displays all arguments and its values from a
                        selected R function
read.all                Read all documents in a folder and subfolders
                        assigning them to the global environment; just
                        extensions ".txt" and ".csv" are allowed
